<PLACEHOLDER: IF_DOCKER>
#### Docker Deployment
- Build image: `docker build -t <PLACEHOLDER: PROJECT_NAME>:latest .`
- Tag image: `docker tag <PLACEHOLDER: PROJECT_NAME>:latest <PLACEHOLDER: PROJECT_NAME>:<version>`
- Push to registry: `docker push <PLACEHOLDER: PROJECT_NAME>:<version>`
- Run container: `docker run -p <PLACEHOLDER: PORTS>:<PLACEHOLDER: PORTS> <PLACEHOLDER: PROJECT_NAME>:latest`
- Run with environment: `docker run --env-file .env <PLACEHOLDER: PROJECT_NAME>:latest`

#### Docker Compose
- Start services: `docker-compose up`
- Start in background: `docker-compose up -d`
- Stop services: `docker-compose down`
- Rebuild and start: `docker-compose up --build`
- View logs: `docker-compose logs -f`
- Scale services: `docker-compose up --scale service-name=3`

<PLACEHOLDER: IF_KUBERNETES>
#### Kubernetes Deployment
- Apply manifests: `kubectl apply -f k8s/`
- Deploy: `kubectl apply -f k8s/deployment.yaml`
- Update deployment: `kubectl rollout restart deployment/<deployment-name>`
- View pods: `kubectl get pods`
- View logs: `kubectl logs -f <pod-name>`
- Port forward: `kubectl port-forward <pod-name> <local-port>:<pod-port>`
- Delete deployment: `kubectl delete -f k8s/deployment.yaml`

#### Helm Deployment
- Install chart: `helm install <release-name> ./charts/<chart-name>`
- Upgrade release: `helm upgrade <release-name> ./charts/<chart-name>`
- Uninstall: `helm uninstall <release-name>`
- List releases: `helm list`
- Get values: `helm get values <release-name>`

