#### Netlify Deployment
- Deploy: `netlify deploy`
- Deploy to production: `netlify deploy --prod`
- Build and deploy: `netlify build && netlify deploy --prod`

<PLACEHOLDER: IF_HEROKU>
#### Heroku Deployment
- Deploy: `git push heroku main`
- Create app: `heroku create <app-name>`
- Set config vars: `heroku config:set KEY=value`
- View logs: `heroku logs --tail`
- Run one-off dyno: `heroku run <command>`

